description: One UN Support to Global Compact and Corporate Social Responsibility

subproject.description: Project aims to seed the idea of the Global Compact and corporate social responsibility among the business community, involving government, academia, trade unions and NGO/CSOs, facilitating learning and sharing of experiences about CSR and implementation of the GC principles, building active collaboration between participants, motivating companies to engage in partnerships and encourage the private sector intermediaries to act as catalysts.
